echo "░██╗░░░░░░░██╗██╗██╗░░██╗██╗███╗░░██╗░██████╗░  ░█████╗░░██████╗
░██║░░██╗░░██║██║██║░██╔╝██║████╗░██║██╔════╝░  ██╔══██╗██╔════╝
░╚██╗████╗██╔╝██║█████═╝░██║██╔██╗██║██║░░██╗░  ██║░░██║╚█████╗░
░░████╔═████║░██║██╔═██╗░██║██║╚████║██║░░╚██╗  ██║░░██║░╚═══██╗
░░╚██╔╝░╚██╔╝░██║██║░╚██╗██║██║░╚███║╚██████╔╝  ╚█████╔╝██████╔╝
░░░╚═╝░░░╚═╝░░╚═╝╚═╝░░╚═╝╚═╝╚═╝░░╚══╝░╚═════╝░  ░╚════╝░╚═════╝░"

echo "-------------------------------"
echo "---     Checking Distro     ---"
echo "-------------------------------"

DISTRO=$(lsb_release -i | cut -d: -f2 | sed s/'^\t'//)
VERSION=$(cat /etc/os-release | grep VERSION_ID | cut -d= -f2)

echo "Distro:" $DISTRO
echo "Version:" $VERSION
